<p>She showed off her look in a video post on MTV's Instagram account of her in their 'virtual video booth.'</p>

<p>The Golden Globe nominee danced against of swirling background of psychedelic colors that looked like the inside of a lava lamp.</p>

<p>Joey first showed off her look on Friday when she posted snaps of it to her Instagram.</p>

<p>She showed herself slipping into the vibrant heels, and other photos gave closeups of her retro dress. </p>

