<p>This year saw the release of the sequel to Joey's hit Netflix romantic comedy The Kissing Booth.</p>

<p>She starred in the film opposite her ex-boyfriend Jacob Elordi, who was featured in the previous installment and also stars on HBO's Euphoria.</p>

<p>In July, it was revealed that a third film in the series had been shot back-to-back with the second in 2019, so fans will get to see a continuation of her romances next year. </p>

